<!-- <reciter /> -->`,r:{minutes:.14,words:41},y:"a",t:"背词器",i:"eye"},[":md"]],["v-6fac4928","/farraginous/recommend_packages.html",{d:16516224e5,l:"2022年5月4日",c:["推荐","教程"],g:["桌面端","移动端","工具"],e:`<h1> 软件汇总</h1>
<p>一些好用软件的推荐。</p>
<ul>
<li>关于 magisk &amp; LSPosed，请移步<a href="/articles/mobile_setting.html#magisk" target="blank">设置手机</a></li>
